-- Valeant to launch exchange offer for Allergan this week
-- By Rod Nickel in Winnipeg
-- Tue Jun 17, 2014 09:12AM EDT
-- None



June 17 (Reuters) - Valeant Pharmaceuticals Inc <VRX.TO> said on Tuesday it will launch an exchange offer for Allergan Inc <AGN.N> this week, allowing it to eventually take the unsolicited bid directly to shareholders.

